{"tid":24842,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲去過關島","createTime":"2016-12-05T18:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T17:33:15.000Z","uid":31257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"889000e357321b76f73df5a5a35f9c1ea58f0e11","tid":24842,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"見到有平機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關島值唔值得去？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f42544f5911a2e09bdcf2ddba7a58e169dcc2b","tid":24842,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"想plan係個度結婚  但又好似無咩好玩"},{"pid":"e5220e5c7cce492d488f46a4244f988400ef2451","tid":24842,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"有諗過去，不過睇過下D資料同東南亞差不多，但貴很多<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb753f6c24f95784a274cab3ba971dbe43e3d6c1","tid":24842,"uid":57582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:33:27.000Z","msg":"關島無hostel,酒店貴到仆街<br />\n雖然琴晚我都買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45760714ff36642416ea1289a8de00b4bc1fefd","tid":24842,"uid":57371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"無車牌係咪唔洗諗?"},{"pid":"294e8847c02992bd1fdcb1de241dee5ab560cf99","tid":24842,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:48:59.000Z","msg":"酒店3星4晚都要3千 但兩個人share都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我見玩水上活動d價錢貴到仆街，百幾蚊美金先玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋上網睇d人話個邊多遊客 同成街都日本人"},{"pid":"f1c10f61ba565de7ea8a4219c7772b3ef161c3b2","tid":24842,"uid":5251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:49:52.000Z","msg":"見到機票好平都想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ed74a0e880ee446427d1844192c215a0f23922","tid":24842,"uid":26969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"買左一月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6960e24621b5e08322aff2dec585bdcd0a788a","tid":24842,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:45:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左一月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己？<br />\n我最後冇買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2319d034c9429e6d5e115333e41b3e4eb63acd28","tid":24842,"uid":26969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買左一月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己？<br />\n我最後冇買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2個去 個到洗費貴"},{"pid":"807481248b8d1885afb18b82ad8a0e798f388fd3","tid":24842,"uid":39767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"夏威夷又點睇?不過機票勁貴"},{"pid":"b63b3d2c47000d2dc42e9ef8306521b0c936a8e3","tid":24842,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夏威夷又點睇?不過機票勁貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係好貴<br />\n返工有錢先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994032d8dc955a8d20b3d72f8904119b043e95ac","tid":24842,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想plan係個度結婚  但又好似無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n之前去左朋友起關島搞既婚禮<br />\n鍾意水上活動就一流<br />\n仲有揸飛機（真係自己揸）<br />\n跳傘<br />\n賽車<br />\nShopping 就唔好有其望<br />\nOutlet ok廢<br />\n野食堅大份<br />\n貴錢同你去outback/ruby Tuesday 差唔多<br />\n洗費唔覺好多"},{"pid":"f4b4b68e2418dc7457fdd06bbe6c3ebdc0c47bba","tid":24842,"uid":18635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:29:40.000Z","msg":"揸飛機超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個度得兩個大型商場 outlet 嘛嘛地啦 <br />\nD野食都ok 又大份<br />\n個障我係買左pass <br />\n類似一個星期任搭 仲要係冷氣巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見有其他公司 但個d巴士係無冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個路線基本上會行晒旅客會去既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左揸飛機個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有真係勁多日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就覺得度假既話都幾寫意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00894b12a89ab18dc853e84788074ec76c44a160","tid":24842,"uid":18635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸飛機超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個度得兩個大型商場 outlet 嘛嘛地啦 <br />\nD野食都ok 又大份<br />\n個障我係買左pass <br />\n類似一個星期任搭 仲要係冷氣巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見有其他公司 但個d巴士係無冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個路線基本上會行晒旅客會去既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左揸飛機個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有真係勁多日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就覺得度假既話都幾寫意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61cf9e5ad18d701cffe95f9226c49ce009e48a3","tid":24842,"uid":26238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"9月去過<br />\n最好自己揸車<br />\n巴士短都4，5usd<br />\n酒店上次住間最雞既都3，400hkd一晚<br />\n睇到海就過千不過住一晚你都覺得不枉此生<br />\n海陸空乜都有<br />\n試過越野車，飛機<br />\n景好靚，不怕貴可以試哂<br />\n1000usd差不多成個trip"},{"pid":"4f3863b547b48829a2f00f81447b915d1bc8ef6d","tid":24842,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c67b031928cc34fc1d4b7fad49c5d75e5ee5c33","tid":24842,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"我12月尾去呀 諗住跳傘"},{"pid":"0a2d2bd13d743adbf0c5510d03a020ac8868ac96","tid":24842,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"抽中左uo免費機但唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c4216638283b957c266ed6d7bbeaf34ffc35fc","tid":24842,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽中左uo免費機但唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜冇得轉讓"},{"pid":"ce77914ef7dd0311205f02f4dcfe1266dbb4ba3c","tid":24842,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:17:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccb3a5c530362637b89a6016f88e0ffae6160ccf","tid":24842,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抽中左uo免費機但唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜冇得轉讓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀 都無跟名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg